<template>
  <el-table
      :data="formDataList"
      v-if="formDataListShow"
      style="width: 100%"
  >
    <el-table-column align="center" label="ID" width="100" type="index">
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="quartersThird"
        label="职位名称"
        width="180"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="graduateName"
        label="学生姓名"
        width="180"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="graduateCollege"
        label="毕业院校"
        width="180"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="enRecentNumber"
        label="所学专业"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        label="操作"
        width="100">
      <template slot-scope="scope">
        <el-button @click="goto(scope.row)" type="text" size="small">查看详情</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-table-column>
  </el-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {

}
</script>
